{"tid":1024970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"77歲做絲打 源於孫女患腦瘤 共留印記免遺忘 意外成網民樹洞","createTime":"2019-02-17T03:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T14:00:04.000Z","uid":100438,"like":434,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5647239c468b643351ae648023e067b80d6a8e1c","tid":1024970,"uid":100438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:46:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190217/s00002/1550340081803/77%e6%ad%b2%e5%81%9a%e7%b5%b2%e6%89%93-%e6%ba%90%e6%96%bc%e5%ad%ab%e5%a5%b3%e6%82%a3%e8%85%a6%e7%98%a4-%e5%85%b1%e7%95%99%e5%8d%b0%e8%a8%98%e5%85%8d%e9%81%ba%e5%bf%98-%e6%84%8f%e5%a4%96%e6%88%90%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91%e6%a8%b9%e6%b4%9e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190217%2Fs00002%2F1550340081803%2F77%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%2581%259a%25e7%25b5%25b2%25e6%2589%2593-%25e6%25ba%2590%25e6%2596%25bc%25e5%25ad%25ab%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e6%2582%25a3%25e8%2585%25a6%25e7%2598%25a4-%25e5%2585%25b1%25e7%2595%2599%25e5%258d%25b0%25e8%25a8%2598%25e5%2585%258d%25e9%2581%25ba%25e5%25bf%2598-%25e6%2584%258f%25e5%25a4%2596%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e6%25b0%2591%25e6%25a8%25b9%25e6%25b4%259e&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=1eb732ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190217%2Fs00002%2F1550340081803%2F77%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%2581%259a%25e7%25b5%25b2%25e6%2589%2593-%25e6%25ba%2590%25e6%2596%25bc%25e5%25ad%25ab%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e6%2582%25a3%25e8%2585%25a6%25e7%2598%25a4-%25e5%2585%25b1%25e7%2595%2599%25e5%258d%25b0%25e8%25a8%2598%25e5%2585%258d%25e9%2581%25ba%25e5%25bf%2598-%25e6%2584%258f%25e5%25a4%2596%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e6%25b0%2591%25e6%25a8%25b9%25e6%25b4%259e&h=33e7522f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190217/s00002/1550340081803/77%e6%ad%b2%e5%81%9a%e7%b5%b2%e6%89%93-%e6%ba%90%e6%96%bc%e5%ad%ab%e5%a5%b3%e6%82%a3%e8%85%a6%e7%98%a4-%e5%85%b1%e7%95%99%e5%8d%b0%e8%a8%98%e5%85%8d%e9%81%ba%e5%bf%98-%e6%84%8f%e5%a4%96%e6%88%90%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91%e6%a8%b9%e6%b4%9e</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】去年仲夏，一眾「巴打絲打」在網上討論區中左看看右看看，盼在海量帖文找一絲慰藉。突然，一絲打自稱77歲，更叫一班網民隨便向她發問。<br />\n<br />\n帖文擦亮了眾人眼球，其實這個婆婆不懂用電腦，也不懂打字，一切出自乖孫的主意。患腦腫瘤的孫女害怕自己在開腦手術後忘記婆婆，決心把相處的時光記下，又在論壇上和婆婆一起「出post」，請大家和婆婆聊天。<br />\n<br />\n婆婆本懼怕學習新事物，但為了讓孫女開心，她衝破自己的安舒區，除了學用智能電話發語音信息、傳照片，更與不認識的網民談天。意想不到的是，二人漸漸成為某些網民的樹洞，為他們解憂，細說如何與家中長輩相處。"},{"pid":"f7b8f82acffc0b8bdaec190d8db17b4f8144305a","tid":1024970,"uid":100438,"like":202,"dislike":1,"score":201,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"2018年7月，LIHKG（連登）討論區上一個「絲（女論壇會員），77歲，你問我答」的帖文，為網民投下震撼彈。起初大家都以為這只是一個年輕屁孩假扮老人家，無數侮辱留言滿天飛，更有人問她用不用穿尿片？怎料婆婆不慌不忙回應：「啋過你！不過醫過癌，有時會好難忍」，她更貼出自己的照片，證明自己是如假包換的婆婆。<br />\n<br />\n一眾網民大感震驚，開始和這個可愛的老人來一場對談，更叫婆婆別把無禮的留言放在心上。記者問怎樣稱呼？雪婆婆先呆了一呆，然後有點害羞地說：「啊！我知道了，我什麼名字嗎？ 時撈（Snow）！」婆婆名字裏有個「雪」字，因此以「Snow」為網名。"},{"pid":"99d6c0a37b68897e9e294b0d6874d83ecedff05c","tid":1024970,"uid":139967,"like":124,"dislike":1,"score":123,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"個原 po  入面啲留言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26f1f576bd8a9faa71a43ada10fd8eaa28a106f","tid":1024970,"uid":9053,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"link!?"},{"pid":"009585729f74c99307c3c6a9859be3f1948ddddd","tid":1024970,"uid":3241,"like":389,"dislike":14,"score":375,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"而家連明報都要係度Mon post....真係而家做妓者係冇水平可言"},{"pid":"ac83f734863be45720459dc7dbc57b97fec5d6d8","tid":1024970,"uid":136662,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"quote":{"pid":"009585729f74c99307c3c6a9859be3f1948ddddd","tid":1024970,"uid":3241,"like":389,"dislike":14,"score":375,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"而家連明報都要係度Mon post....真係而家做妓者係冇水平可言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"遲下到香港<br />\n行政長官看手錶"},{"pid":"7a740b7d3373dcb2de51cdc07292a3f224d2573c","tid":1024970,"uid":89530,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"quote":{"pid":"99d6c0a37b68897e9e294b0d6874d83ecedff05c","tid":1024970,"uid":139967,"like":124,"dislike":1,"score":123,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"個原 po  入面啲留言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"冇追過都估到入面啲留言有幾難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca4653cd463a0c9da788bcfd69e8974b506043b","tid":1024970,"uid":3457,"like":334,"dislike":2,"score":332,"quote":{"pid":"7a740b7d3373dcb2de51cdc07292a3f224d2573c","tid":1024970,"uid":89530,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"quote":{"pid":"99d6c0a37b68897e9e294b0d6874d83ecedff05c","tid":1024970,"uid":139967,"like":124,"dislike":1,"score":123,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"個原 po  入面啲留言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"冇追過都估到入面啲留言有幾難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"實有痴線留言 <br />\n77歲幫唔幫含撚 <br />\n個口冇牙一定好爽依類痴媽根野"},{"pid":"2aee5d5ac6176cda7e0b8dc23cc5da618de04614","tid":1024970,"uid":25494,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"009585729f74c99307c3c6a9859be3f1948ddddd","tid":1024970,"uid":3241,"like":389,"dislike":14,"score":375,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"而家連明報都要係度Mon post....真係而家做妓者係冇水平可言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"全世界得你可以上連登？<br />\n你唔比記者都係連登仔黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76322097db243d85151a322ab4042a9b4d767061","tid":1024970,"uid":228963,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd625132826c407a1a433376165ed7306ef42e9a","tid":1024970,"uid":147376